{
  "page": "Gunthor (disambiguation)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/index.php/Gunthor\" title=\"Gunthor\">Gunthor</a></b> is a chief of the Stone Crows.\n</p><p>Other characters named <b>Gunthor</b> include:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Gunthor_Darklyn\" title=\"Gunthor Darklyn\">Gunthor Darklyn</a>, Lord of Duskendale and head of House Darklyn during the Dance of the Dragons</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gunthor_Estermont\" title=\"Gunthor Estermont\">Gunthor Estermont</a>, a knight of House Estermont</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gunthor_Goodbrother\" title=\"Gunthor Goodbrother\">Gunthor Goodbrother</a>, a member of House Goodbrother during the Dance of the Dragons</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gunthor_Hightower\" title=\"Gunthor Hightower\">Gunthor Hightower</a>, a son of Lord Leyton Hightower</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gunthor_Royce\" title=\"Gunthor Royce\">Gunthor Royce</a>, Lord of Runestone and head of House Royce during the regency of King Aegon III Targaryen</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gunthor_(disambiguation)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Guthor_Grimm\" title=\"Guthor Grimm\">Guthor Grimm</a>, the Lord of Greyshield</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404091254\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.003 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.003 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5